{"tid":982121,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"第5集第6集導演繼續執導《職業特工隊》連拍第7集第8集","createTime":"2019-01-15T00:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T03:02:49.000Z","uid":41343,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"f1d894fb69441d9133a165dfc2c6daf0f0145bb2","tid":982121,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T00:13:03.000Z","msg":"After delivering the biggest box office hit in the &ldquo;Mission: Impossible&rdquo; franchise, Paramount Pictures is ready to continue being in business with director Christopher McQuarrie in a big way.<br />\n<br />\nSources tell Variety that McQuarrie has signed back on to return to write and direct the next two films in the popular franchise. Sources also add that both films would be shot back-to-back &mdash; not unlike the final two &ldquo;Avengers&rdquo; sequels &mdash; in order to take advantage of the popularity of the series, with the first bowing summer 2021 and the second coming out in summer 2022. The release comes in 2021 to avoid conflict with Paramount and Cruise&rsquo;s next big venture, &ldquo;Top Gun: Maverick.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nMcQuarrie had said in recent interviews he was hoping to do something different and had been meeting on a handful of projects including Paramount&rsquo;s &ldquo;Without Remorse&rdquo; starring Michael B. Jordan as John Clark. With the latest &ldquo;Mission: Impossible&rdquo; film grossing over $790 million worldwide, the best haul in the franchise to date, the studio knew they couldn&rsquo;t let a good thing die and quickly moved to bring back McQuarrie to write and direct the next two installments.<br />\n<br />\nMcQuarrie will now look to start writing the script while Cruise continues to shoot &ldquo;Top Gun: Maverick.&rdquo; While no start date is set yet, sources indicate the studio would intend to start shooting sometime in 2019.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://variety.com/2019/film/news/christopher-mcquarrie-mission-impossible-films-back-to-back-1202986902/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2019%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fchristopher-mcquarrie-mission-impossible-films-back-to-back-1202986902%2F&d=SapV93%2BIpUVg07QGamfIC8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=7d33dbda\" target=\"_blank\">https://variety.com/2019/film/news/christopher-mcquarrie-mission-impossible-films-back-to-back-1202986902/</a>"},{"pid":"dc9f18bab7e541c6cd4ea7610dc3a39c0c8371f5","tid":982121,"uid":172802,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T00:45:10.000Z","msg":"湯哥上山下海乜都拍過晒，再拍真係要上宇宙打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然係咁但係都好鍾意呢個系列，希望第一任老婆同而加條女都繼續留任Rebecca Ferguson <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75e9fad4d2cbb010de4556ed790b59040543548","tid":982121,"uid":2811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T00:46:49.000Z","msg":"繼續串連Tom Cruise啲動作場面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73270732f53284f9ea2bc6918c5510033008206d","tid":982121,"uid":20522,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T00:46:51.000Z","msg":"湯告魯斯仲有咩牌可以考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80ea68b3fda739a24d50ec61377c81ef98f5251","tid":982121,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T01:29:42.000Z","msg":"再拍變Tom Cruise退休作<br />\n收手好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be0b175f542cb56493ec9440a8c3ee46bfaa45e","tid":982121,"uid":37759,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T01:48:23.000Z","msg":"下次湯爺會唔會玩到企係部f22上面遙控部f22去追前面部f22<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360ead1dcf52ef0d1d15786d6a56791fadf0b9d9","tid":982121,"uid":61331,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cit